        <item>
            <title>打麻雀机械人登场，机械臂打牌 + 能自主研判牌局</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/majongrobot/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=majongrobot</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/majongrobot/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 30 Apr 2025 12:35:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305535</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>平时放假最惨是三缺一无脚一齐打牌。现在中国人工智能公司灵初智能科技公司 PsiBot 展示了一个具备高阶推理、长程操作能力的机械人 Psi-R1。机械人能在变化快速、环境开放的现实场景中打麻雀，并展现灵活操作和自主决策能力。PsiBot 利用自主研发的分层端到端模型 Psi-R1，结合类人推理方式与强化学习框架，成功实现 CoAT（Chain of Action Thought）思维系统，并在麻雀桌上执行出牌、碰牌与胡牌等策略性决策。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir108screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir108screenshot-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir108screenshot-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir108screenshot.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Psi-R1 在最新展示中透过感应器进行精细操作，准确抓取和翻动麻雀牌，其动作节奏虽慢，但整体过程与人类玩家极为相似。机械人不单只执行物理动作，更可进行连贯的逻辑推理。每次出牌前，Psi-R1 都会经历完整思考流程，包括判断手中牌面组合、计算风险与收益、预测对手出牌，再决定是否执行碰牌、杠牌或胡牌操作。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1028screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305538" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1028screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1028screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1028screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1048screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1048screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1048screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1048screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在 PsiBot 的影片中，Psi-R1 能根据对手出的一筒判断自己拥有两张一筒，具备碰牌资格，因此执行碰牌行动，目标是加快听牌进程。其判断逻辑包括：「从我手牌来看，不应该争取清一色，碰是目前为胡牌作最好准备。」这一思考程序让机械人能如人类般审视局势，自主调整战术。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1057screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1057screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1057screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1057screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>更特别的是，Psi-R1 能在游戏进行中变更策略。例如原定打出六筒，但抽到七筒后，计算条牌牌型已成顺子，自行改变计划并宣布自摸胡牌。这样的决策过程说明机械人不仅拥有记忆和模拟人脑思维能力，更能在实时互动中适应变化，作出合适行动。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1120screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305537" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1120screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1120screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1120screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PsiBot 表示，这项技术展示机械人已达到 L3 等级的智慧行动能力，可支援复杂多变的场景操作。麻将只是其应用案例之一，未来目标是将该系统应用至工业生产、零售服务、物流配送和家居环境等领域，发挥长时间稳定执行的潜力。</p><p>除了单机能力外，Psi-R1 亦展现人-机、机-机与机-环境三重交互协作的功能。影片中，两部 PsiBot 机械人能彼此沟通、交换资讯并协作完成打牌任务，提升整体策略智慧。当中机械人甚至能模拟情绪表情，增加牌桌互动性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir119screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir119screenshot-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir119screenshot-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir119screenshot.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1128screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1128screensho-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1128screensho-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlapsir1128screensho.jpg 1272w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PsiBot 期望透过麻将这项复杂游戏，向大众呈现其机械人在自主学习、长时推理及人类级操作能力上的进展。这一突破令「三缺一」的情况或许再不是问题，未来打麻雀可能有机械人自动上桌应战。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_21222"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OfwtXkvRuEQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：YouTube</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/30/majongrobot/fun-tech/">打麻雀机械人登场，机械臂打牌 + 能自主研判牌局</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
